thread.title: David

author: David
title: David
text:
The cover is exactly what I was after. It's slightly bigger than necessary for the Starlet, but has an excellent tie down strap that fits under the middle of the car, ensring that the cover will not come off in strong winds. It also features a zip opening that can be useful to access the car without removing the cover.
Delivery was prompt and the packaging ensured the contents arrived undamaged.
